import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.sort_values(by='time')
    plt.plot(data['time'], data['count'])
    plt.title('What is the overall trend of count over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['count'].plot(kind='hist', bins=20, color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].mean(), color='red', label='Mean')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].median(), color='green', label='Median')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of count?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['day_of_week'] = pd.Categorical(data['day_of_week'], categories=['Monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday', 'Sunday'], ordered=True)
    data = data.sort_values('day_of_week')
    data = data.groupby('day_of_week').mean()
    plt.bar(data.index, data['count'])
    plt.title('What is the average count per day of the week?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Day of the week')
    plt.ylabel('Average count')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.boxplot(data.groupby('hour')['count'].apply(list), showfliers=False)
    ax.set_xticklabels(range(24))
    ax.set_xlabel('Hour')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of count by hour?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):

    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.scatter(data['day_of_week'], data['count'], alpha=0.5)
    ax.set_xlabel('Day of the Week')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.set_title('What is the relationship between count and day of the week?')
    return plt
